g.data-name: Transporter ko roz roz ka hisab btane ki ab zaroorat nahi
Apne roz ke hisab kharche ki report SMS aur Whatsapp dwara transporter ko bhejein
Mahino ka roz ka aur har ek trip ka hisab dekhe
Apne khate ko apni hi bhasha mein app dwara dale
Roz ke sabhi kharcho ko apne phone dwara manage kare
